Evaluation-Only Notice

The materials in this repository are provided for research review, educational discussion, and reproducibility-oriented evaluation.

They are not provided as an engine-design tool, propulsion-performance predictor, flight controller, hazardous-experiment guide, propellant-handling guide, aerospace safety system, or commercial technology.

Any applied, experimental, aerospace, safety-critical, industrial, or hazardous use requires independent expert review, high-fidelity validation, domain-specific safety assessment, and appropriate legal/regulatory review.

